{"tid":1728760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日繼續停課！","createTime":"2019-11-17T04:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:18:56.000Z","uid":211578,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8bd07b9a89b356c4438f1b2fc2d2494a64652d","tid":1728760,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:10:40.000Z","msg":"教育局指，雖然全港道路及公共運輸服務逐步恢復，但目前尚有不穩定因素，而星期一亦是周末後第一個繁忙的工作日，基於安全考慮，全港學校（包括幼稚園、小學、中學及特殊學校）明日（十一月十八日）繼續停課， 並應為日後復課作好準備。"},{"pid":"d1bdf0c0333699f95755b0b5a52bfce225464da3","tid":1728760,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:11:05.000Z","msg":"政府中計！"},{"pid":"a80377f7e492def4e366c15ffa08473b5d46d6a5","tid":1728760,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:11:27.000Z","msg":"又跌入自己個圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c030cec54d1911e3507b2cc5a1011a8f33fefe0","tid":1728760,"uid":114090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:12:06.000Z","msg":"停課的寶寶都要出來搭車同搭免費船呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上星期四五無人排隊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d95ac6671ee79b461fb096da258d1d56ea8a92b","tid":1728760,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:12:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>他們在打的是「中共政權保衛戰」，而你們僅僅是在打「香港生活方式保衛戰」</strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，<strong>第一就是分化</strong>，<strong>把勇武派、和理非派拆分</strong>，<strong>第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」</strong>，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後<strong>隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒</strong>。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，<strong>但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能</strong>，坦白說，<strong>還是太嫩</strong>。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是<strong>北京</strong>要製造的<strong>焦點轉移</strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"90fc458d831440d80ad93da939def39318263917","tid":1728760,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"唔洗返學都要繼續塞鐵呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1847d08e56110fc198a743213a03909784d7b94c","tid":1728760,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:14:01.000Z","msg":"係咪剩係得我一個on99,每朝等開花<br />\n<br />\n［中場檢討］ 係黎明行動，唔係黃昏行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8653f7daf6add8f51621aa4980cfbaccae0106b3","tid":1728760,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:17:04.000Z","msg":"教育局表示，如情況許可，學校最快將於星期二（19日）復課，請留意教育局進一步公布。<br />\n<br />\n復你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c8e8d33281f6488ddde6179be432b3b4001f6e","tid":1728760,"uid":308850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:18:56.000Z","msg":"不能復課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}